quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  107,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  107,1,bhala tum ne is shakhs ko dekha jo ( rozِ ) jaza ko jhutlata hai ?
  107,2,"yeh wohi ( badbakht ) hai, jo yateem ko dhakkay deta hai"
  107,3,aur faqeer ko khana khilanay ke liye ( logon ko ) targheeb nahi deta
  107,4,to aisay nmazyon ki kharabi hai
  107,5,jo namaz ki taraf se ghaafil rehtay hain
  107,6,jo riya kaari karte hain
  107,7,aur baratnay ki cheeze ariyatan nahi dete
